Automated JDownloader2 and MegaBasterd Proxy Lists
Copyright (C) 2026 Robert Riordan

This repository provides automation for collecting, validating, and exporting
public proxy lists in formats intended for JDownloader2 and MegaBasterd.

This project builds on and was informed by prior work, including:

- imwaitingnow/JDownloader2-jdproxies-creator
  https://github.com/imwaitingnow/JDownloader2-jdproxies-creator

- MuRongPIG/Proxy-Master
  https://github.com/MuRongPIG/Proxy-Master
  Released under the GNU General Public License v3.0.

Additional source references and prior art:

- TheSpeedX/PROXY-List
  https://github.com/TheSpeedX/PROXY-List

- masterofobzene/JDproxygenerator
  https://github.com/masterofobzene/JDproxygenerator

Generated lists contain public, third-party network endpoints. They are provided
without any guarantee of availability, performance, anonymity, legality, or
fitness for a particular purpose.
